/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a car on the road, providing a driver's eye view of the scene. The street is flanked by buildings on both sides, their facades bathed in the soft glow of the day. Power lines crisscross above, forming a network of geometric patterns against the sky. Trees line the street, their green foliage adding a touch of nature to the urban landscape. The sky above is a clear blue, with a smattering of clouds adding depth to the expansive backdrop. The image is taken from a low angle, which emphasizes the height of the buildings and the expanse of the sky. The colors in the image are predominantly gray, green, and blue, reflecting the blend of urban architecture and natural elements.
